race for your life , charlie brown ! is a 1977 american animated adventure comedy film produced by united feature syndicate for paramount pictures , directed by bill melendez and phil roman , and the third in a series of films based on the peanuts comic strip . it was the first peanuts feature-length film produced after the death of composer vince guaraldi and used the same voice cast from the 1975 tv special , you 're a good sport , charlie brown . the film received generally positive reviews from critics and audiences , and came five years after snoopy , come home , and three years before bon voyage , charlie brown ( and do n't come back !! ) .